                <h1 class="book-now-title">Book here now!</h1>
                <p class="book-now-text">Give yourself and your partner a peacefull and wonderful room to enjoy.</p>
                <a href="https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/1156623638372071033?guests=1&adults=1&s=67&unique_share_id=2e6a92f4-6268-4770-9427-53f33c891c0c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="book-now"> Book Now in Airbnb</a>
